ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">talked</a> a <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34979401.287353/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmx=
vb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDEtMDMvY3J5cHRvLW1hbmlwdWxhdG=
