YWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB75389fdb" itemprop=3D"StoryLi=
nk" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text=
-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color=
: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">times</a> a=
bout Avi Eisenberg, who did a straightforward and rather funny manipulation=
 of a decentralized finance platform called Mango Markets. (Briefly: He set=
 up two accounts on Mango=E2=80=99s platform to trade futures contracts, he=
 sold a bunch of futures on Mango=E2=80=99s own MNGO token from one account=
, he=C2=A0<em>bought=C2=A0</em>all those futures in another account, he wen=
t and bought spot MNGO on another platform to drive up the price of MNGO, h=
e borrowed against his long futures position on Mango, he cashed out about =
$110 million and walked away from his losing position.)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Eisenberg=E2=80=99s problem is that=C2=A0<em>h=
e=C2=A0</em>thought that Mango was a Fun Crypto Market but, for instance, U=
S prosecutors think it=E2=80=99s a Nice One. He was arrested and goes on tr=
ial this week; <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/349=
79401.287353/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMD=
QtMDgvY3J5cHRvLXNjYW0tY3JpbWluYWwtdHJpYWwtdGVzdHMtY29kZS1pcy1sYXctY2xhaW0tY=
